Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:34.38,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Your defenceless sleeping face tightens my chest so much
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:34.95,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.44,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem knows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:39.18,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even if Subaru hates himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:41.38,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.13,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,All the good things about you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.06,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem believes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.50,Translation - Subaru,,0,0,0,,Why this much…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.66,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Just how much do you know about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.41,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The Subaru that Rem sees…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:53.50,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,You're a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:56.78,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,When I was stuck in a world not knowing who I was, you were the one who rescued me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.67,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,To let my sister and me escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.13,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,And went up against the Mabeasts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.03,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The words I wanted to hear the most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:05.37,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The time when I wanted to hear those words the most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:09.03,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The words I wanted to hear the most by the person I wanted to hear from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.98,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem's time was stopped for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.23,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,From that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:15.86,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The heart that was frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:18.12,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,You were the one who gently moved them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.62,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even when nobody believes in Subaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.43,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even when you're about to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.15,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even when you no longer believe in yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.32,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)}Rem will believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.86,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The Subaru who saved Rem is a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.23,Translation - Subaru,,0,0,0,,I didn't save anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.86,Translation - Subaru,,0,0,0,,No one even expects anything from me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.77,Translation - Subaru,,0,0,0,,I hate myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.12,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem is here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:38.19,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I'm here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:40.42,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The same Rem that Subaru saved
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:41.46,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem is here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.46,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I will listen to anything Subaru wants to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.12,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I want to hear, that's why
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.49,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I love you, Subaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:49.67,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,When you pat on my head, I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.85,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Whenever I hear you speak, I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.50,Translation - Subaru,,0,0,0,,Is someone like me okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.62,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want it to be anyone else but you, Subaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.38,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Subaru, the way your eyes glistens, I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.57,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Subaru's way of walking, I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.68,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Please show me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.85,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,The cool side of my hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.48,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Rem loves you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.15,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even if you're empty, even if you have nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:11.21,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't forgive yourself, let's restart from beginning right here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.63,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Just like that time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.30,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,When Subaru moved it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.98,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,When I thought my time was frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.41,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,We'll move yours now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.05,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,Let's begin from here on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:22.47,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,From square one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.86,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:26.92,Translation - Rem,,0,0,0,,From Zero
